text: Kati Kati is a 2016 Kenyan German drama movie directed by Mbithi Masya and starring Nyokabi Gethaiga, Elsaphan Njora, Paul Ogola, Peter Nzioki, Fidelis Nyambura Mukundi, Brian Ogola, Mumbi Maina. == Other websites == * Category:2016 drama movies Category:Kenyan movies Category:German drama movies
